<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans II. von Degenberg, Viztum von Amberg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, wegen eines Hofs Georg Stromers, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_84" id="40v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_84_r1l9"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hanſen vom degenberg</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l10">vicʒtumb cʒu Amperg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_84_r1l11"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> wicʒtumb wicʒtumb wir ſenden cʒu ew hanſen Mawrer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dẏener mit ew cʒu reden von <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> kuntſchafft wegen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l13">deʒ hofs / da 
<del rend="strikethrough">vormals </del> Görg 
<del rend="strikethrough"> er </del> Stromeyr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l14">vnd Ratgeſelle vormals mit ewch auch von geredt hat / . vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_84_r1l15"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_84" id="40v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen vom Degenberg, vicztumb czu Amperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan> wicztumb, wir senden czu
                                                ew Hansen Mawrer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                                                dyener, mit ew czu reden von
                                                  <expan>ein<ex>er</ex></expan> kuntschafft wegen
                                                dez hofs, da Görg Stromeyr,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber burger und
                                                ratgeselle, vormals mit ewch auch von geredt hat und
                                                  <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
